name: I see you - pop art animated version
description: Ink and pencil drawing manipulated and animated. 404x720 px, 24sec .mov file . I see you- I see the surface and the wild that lingers within. I see your radiant beating heart and the love that resides. I see strength, compassion, the king, the warrior, the mystic, and the quipster. I see the devotion to self and spirit. I see and my God, you are magnificent.
